FBIS4-33545 "drlat110_a_94010" FBIS-LAT-94-110 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba CPC Delegation Lays Wreath at Monument CPC Delegation Lays Wreath at Monument FL0806002494 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 1952 GMT 7 Jun 94 FL0806002494 Havana Radio Reloj Network Spanish BFN [Text] On 7 June, the Chinese Communist Party delegation laid a wreath at the monument to the Chinese who fought in Cuba's wars of independence a century ago. In the square at Vina and L street in Havana, there is a modest monument to our Asian brothers who during the great struggle for freedom did not defect or betray the cause.
